<br></br><br></br>
<b>ORDER DETAILS</b>
<br></br>
Information relating to your order can be found in your signed contract. Please take a look at this to double check that the details are correct. If you need to discuss anything, please contact me.
<br></br>
<br></br>
<b>WHAT WE ARE DOING NOW</b>
<br></br>
