<br></br><br></br>
Did you know that you can see the latest updates and track your <apex:outputLink value="http://www.virginmediabusiness.co.uk/help/s/trackorder"> order online</apex:outputLink>?  You will need your Order ID, which was supplied to you on your confirmation email, but if you don't have one, just let our team know.
<br></br><br></br>
